- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the use of satellite images and machine learning for identifying informal settlements in cities.
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also likely as the paper discusses the spatial characteristics of informal settlements and their relationship to services and infrastructure.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper proposes a novel machine learning approach for identifying and predicting informal settlements.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a possible category as the paper discusses the implications of identifying informal settlements for policymakers and governments in developing countries.
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a less likely category as the paper does not discuss any security or cryptography-related topics.
